data.description:
Welcome to your dream oasis in the heart of Plantation! This captivating single-family home, nestled on an oversized corner lot in the tranquil cul-de-sac of the non-HOA community, Royal Palm Estates, invites you to experience the epitome of Florida living.Boasting a seamless one-story design, this residence offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms within an open floor plan that effortlessly blends style and functionality and includes a jacuzzi tub in second bathroom. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring an extended island with sleek black granite countertops and state-of-the-art modern appliances, setting the stage for memorable gatherings and delectable meals. Step into the inviting Florida room, adorned with French doors that open to a private patio, pool and a backyard retreat, perfect for entertaining or unwinding in the sunshine. The master bedroom, with its ensuite bathroom, provides a sanctuary of comfort and luxury.

Immerse yourself in the outdoor paradise of your fenced backyard, complete with a sparkling pool that promises endless hours of relaxation and recreation. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this space is destined to become the heart of your home.

Convenience is key, and this residence offers easy access to major thoroughfares, including the Turnpike and I-95. Explore the surrounding areas of Wellington, Boynton Beach, and Downtown West Palm Beach, or bask in the sun at the nearby stunning beaches. With three international airports just a short drive away, your travel aspirations are within effortless reach.

This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the warmth, elegance, and convenience that define this unique property in the sought-after Royal Palm Estates. Your South Florida paradise awaits - schedule your showing today!
